# Vite env for Auditoo web app. Copy to `apps/web/.env`.
# Server secrets live in `apps/api/.env` only. Overview: repo `.env.example`, docs/SETUP.md §2.

# Local dev must use the local API (below). Pointing at a deployed API while Supabase in apps/api/.env is local gives 401 (JWT issuer mismatch).
# Production (Vercel): set VITE_API_URL=/api — the API is co-hosted on the same domain via a serverless function at api/[[...route]].ts.
VITE_API_URL=http://localhost:3001
